{"tid":1249894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【長輩圖材質】譴責警方不盡責放任示威者癱瘓政治部門","createTime":"2019-06-22T00:36:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T01:24:06.000Z","uid":258197,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"14f0f8515b250dd9c8123a5f55443ee3ed0ead6f","tid":1249894,"uid":258197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:36:34.000Z","msg":"琴日警犬比我地圍足一日都無行動，代表<br />\n（A）證明612使用過高武力；<br />\n如果唔認同（A），仍然認為當日係使用適當武力，即係<br />\n（B）唔盡責維護社會秩序<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成班犬有槍有棍full gear仲想扮弱者一方有冇咁肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我剩係睇到班犬612咁狼死，而家放軟手腳係度扮死狗搏同情個畫面真係好難睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黑警可恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78e86011266b4c356b10c81205bf1fc7c138895a","tid":1249894,"uid":258197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:39:42.000Z","msg":"仲可以借勢話埋唔清場先導致白車單野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3c5037fcea94ad6459444680afc20ddb69a722","tid":1249894,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T01:17:46.000Z","msg":"兩邊不是人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bebea411ba3b83472c5a223628b765059a75a516","tid":1249894,"uid":229460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T01:21:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9f73e66565fcbb1a3e787ce1f15a404cee8cb8a","tid":1249894,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T01:22:47.000Z","msg"